<ol>
<li>Pinto, B., Machado, A.M., Cordeiro, J.M., Malakpour Kolbadinezhad, S., Fonseca, E.m, Andrade, J.P., Palma, J., Ruivo, R., Monteiro, N., <strong>Wilson , J.M.</strong>, and Castro, L.F.C. (2023). Extensive gene loss parallels kidney aglomerulism in Syngnathidae. <em>Current Biology</em> (accepted)</li>
