<li>Kolbadinezhad, S.M., Hajimoradloo, A., Ghorbani, R., Joshaghani, H., <strong>Wilson, J.M.</strong> (2022) Effect of Short-term Elevation Temperature and Salinity Stress on Caspian Roach, <em>Rutilus caspicus</em>. <em>Aquaculture and Fisheries Studies</em> 4(1): 1-10.</li>
<li><u>Moffatt, K., Rossi, M., Park, E.</u>, Svendsen, J.C. and <strong>Wilson, J.M.</strong> (2021). Inhibition of gastric acid secretion with omeprazole affects fish specific dynamic action and growth rate: implications for the development of phenotypic stomach loss. <em>Frontiers in Physiology</em> 13: 966447.</li>
