<li>Lawrence, M., Grayson, P., Jeffrey, J, Docker, M, Garroway, C., <strong>Wilson, J.M.</strong>, Manzon, R, Wilkie, M., Jeffries, K. (2022). Variation in the transcriptome response and detoxification gene diversity drives pesticide tolerance in fishes. <em>Environmental Science &amp; Technology</em> 56, 17, 12137&#8211;12147</li>
<li>Nash, M.T., Quijada-Rodriguez A.R., Allen, G.P.J., <strong>Wilson, J.M.</strong> and Weihrauch, D. (2022). Characterization of 3 different types of aquaporins in <em>Carcinus maenas</em> and their potential role in osmoregulation. <em>Comparative Biochemistry and Physiology</em> A 272: 111281.</li>
<li><u>Tunnah, L.</u>, <strong>Wilson, J.M</strong>., and Wright, P.A. (2022). Retention of larval skin traits in adult amphibious killifishes: A cross-species investigation. <em>Journal of Comparative Physiology B </em><strong>192</strong>: 473&#8211;488. <em>DOI </em><span><a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/s00360-022-01436-7"><em>https://doi.org/10.1007/s00360-022-01436-7</em></a></span></li>
