<li>Borowiec, B.G., Birceanu, O., <strong>Wilson, J.M.</strong>, McDonald, A.E., and Wilkie, M.P. (2022). Niclosamide is a much more potent inhibitor of mitochondrial respiration than TFM in invasive sea lamprey (<em>Petromyzon marinus</em>). ET&amp;C Environ. Sci. Technol. 2022, 56, 8, 4970&#8211;4979. https://doi.org/10.1021/acs.est.1c07117</li>
